    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this absolute gem. Seriously, you have to see it to believe it\u2014it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it spotless and tucked away. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
