    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-tier condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six independent throttle bodies and a high-revving valvetrain. The engine has undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement to ensure mechanical longevity. The chassis is structurally pristine, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement to address the platform's known weak points. Handling is dictated by factory-spec dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension maintain original kinematic precision. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock that remains tight and responsive. Zero fluid seepage, original paint depth, and a cabin free of typical bolster wear. A mechanically transparent example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
