    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear or bolster compression, and the interior retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It has been maintained exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive, documented service history available for your review. The engine bay is pristine, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity to own a 'time capsule' example of this model. We welcome and encourage pre-purchase inspections at any local specialist to confirm its peerless condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
